        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Joab's men.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " The men who formed his regular attendants, and to whose number belonged the ten armour bearers who slew Absalom (",
        "children": []
