      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Samuel 18:15",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Joab retained their command, and probably they would not have served under any other person. It is evident from the enumeration in this verse that the \"men of Judah,\" after escorting David to Jerusalem, had all dispersed to their own homes. 2 Samuel 20:7",
